Imported yachts will be exempt from paying customs duties.
The Ministry of Economic Development intends to temporarily exempt imported yachts and other floating facilities for recreation and sports from customs duties and taxes.
Corresponding changes to the list of preferential goods for temporary duty-free import were prepared by the Ministry on behalf of the Government of the Russian Federation.
Elena Lashkina, Assistant Minister of Economic Development, told Izvestia about this.
